{"id": 171, "genre": 1000, "title": "朋友圈里有哪些不让人讨厌的行为？", "description": "搜集“朋友圈里令人烦心的行为”简直太容易，素材数不胜数；而想找一些让人开心舒服的行为就真的很难找……这个发现本身好像也挺悲情的啊。\r\n", "record_count": 3391, "comment_count": 52, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183647rWXy7a0TxbKEIhBf.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-12-02T08:28:14Z", "questions": [{"id": 138, "title": "朋友圈里有哪些不让人讨厌的行为？", "content": "朋友圈里有哪些不让人讨厌的行为？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 1162, "content": "放宠物照片或者视频", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192600EwBQWJuNr4VUt30l.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1163, "content": "发放滴滴红包", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193508UAg0RLxqK6mjJNWS.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1164, "content": "发布自己的糗事", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193946tgrus0XPV56TfaYj.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1165, "content": "给出10字以上评论而非“哈哈哈哈哈”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192600vDpub5OfAlIHe9Wg.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1166, "content": "推荐好用东西的，同时不自拍及搞代购", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193454U1SXAMB2PgIcvq94.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1167, "content": "持犀利观点的吐槽王", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193327AlXBqZmNr1e7MWfO.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1168, "content": "没有", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182916HUCiw8dZIFu4KDtV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}